CLAUDE-CODE-IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN.md
PROJECT: Cursive Website - Complete SEO/AEO Optimization
SITE: https://meetcursive.com
FRAMEWORK: Next.js (App Router)
HOSTING: Vercel
GOAL: Fix critical rendering issues, expand content, achieve page 1 rankings for target keywords

CRITICAL CONTEXT FOR CLAUDE
Current Site State
28 pages with metadata currently exist
18 blog posts including 5 competitor comparisons
Structured data exists but renders client-side only (BROKEN)
Site Health Score: 45/100 (CRITICAL)
Content Score: 33/100 (MAJOR GAP)
AEO Score: 36/100 (AI visibility blocked)
470 issues affecting 376 pages
24 critical issues, 92 high-priority issues
The Core Technical Problem
The site uses client-side rendering which means:

Content loads AFTER JavaScript executes
Search engines see empty pages (0 words detected on 25 pages)
Internal links don't appear in HTML source
Structured data doesn't render for crawlers
Result: Google can't index the site properly
What Success Looks Like
All content renders in initial HTML (before JavaScript)
Internal links visible in page source (curl test passes)
Structured data in <head> before any client code
Every page has 800+ words of server-rendered content
Breadcrumbs on every page with BreadcrumbList schema
Comprehensive internal linking (5-10 links per page minimum)
TESTING & VERIFICATION COMMANDS
Before marking any task complete, run these tests:

Test 1: Server-Side Rendering Check
curl -s https://meetcursive.com/[page-url] | grep -o "<h1[^>]*>.*</h1>"

Expected: Should return the H1 tag with content
Failure: Returns nothing or empty tag

Test 2: Internal Links Check
curl -s https://meetcursive.com/[page-url] | grep -c "<a href="

Expected: Should return 10+ (navigation + contextual links)
Failure: Returns 0-5

Test 3: Structured Data Check
curl -s https://meetcursive.com/[page-url] | grep "application/ld+json"

Expected: Should return script tags with JSON-LD
Failure: Returns nothing

Test 4: Word Count Check
curl -s https://meetcursive.com/[page-url] | html2text | wc -w

Expected: 800+ words for main pages, 2,500+ for educational content
Failure: Less than 500 words

Test 5: Meta Tags Check
curl -s https://meetcursive.com/[page-url] | grep -E "<meta (name|property)="

Expected: Returns title, description, OG tags, Twitter cards
Failure: Missing any meta tags

PHASE 1: CRITICAL TECHNICAL FIXES (DO FIRST)
Priority: BLOCKING ALL SEO PROGRESS - MUST BE FIXED BEFORE ANY CONTENT WORK
TASK 1.1: Convert All Pages to Server-Side Rendering
Objective: Ensure all content, links, and text appear in initial HTML before JavaScript executes

