TASK 1.2: Fix Internal Linking Architecture
Objective: Add server-rendered internal links to every page so crawlers can discover the entire site

Current Problem:

"No internal links detected" on 25 pages
Navigation may render client-side only
No contextual links within page content
Solution: Add comprehensive internal linking

Step 1: Fix Navigation Component
File: app/components/Navigation.tsx (or wherever nav lives)

// Navigation MUST render server-side with real <a> tags
