        <section id="use-cases">
          <h2>Use Cases for Website Visitor Identification</h2>
          
          <h3>1. B2B Lead Generation</h3>
          <p>
            Identify high-intent prospects researching your product and reach 
            out before they contact competitors.
          </p>
          <ul>
