# Cursive - B2B Lead Generation Platform
https://meetcursive.com

## About
Cursive is a full-stack B2B lead generation platform that identifies anonymous website visitors, enriches them with verified contact data, and automates personalized outreach across email, LinkedIn, SMS, and direct mail. We help B2B companies convert 70% of anonymous website traffic into qualified leads.

## Core Features

- Website Visitor Identification: /visitor-identification
  Identify 70% of anonymous website visitors with names, emails, phone numbers, and job titles—without requiring form fills.

- AI-Powered Outreach: /platform
  Our AI SDR writes personalized emails, LinkedIn messages, and SMS campaigns that convert at 3-5x industry average.

- Intent Data: /intent-audiences
  Know exactly when prospects are researching solutions like yours across the web, not just on your site.

- Audience Builder: /audience-builder
  Segment identified visitors by company, industry, job title, behavior, and intent signals.

- Direct Mail Automation: /direct-mail
  Send personalized postcards and handwritten notes to high-intent prospects automatically.

- CRM Integration: /integrations
  Native integrations with Salesforce, HubSpot, and 200+ other tools.

## Educational Content

- What is Website Visitor Identification: /what-is-website-visitor-identification
  Complete guide to website visitor identification technology, methods, accuracy rates, and implementation.

- What is B2B Intent Data: /what-is-b2b-intent-data
  Learn how B2B intent data works, data sources, accuracy, and use cases for sales and marketing.

- What is an AI SDR: /what-is-ai-sdr
  Comprehensive guide to AI Sales Development Representatives, capabilities, and ROI.

- What is Lead Enrichment: /what-is-lead-enrichment
  How lead enrichment works, data sources, accuracy rates, and implementation best practices.

- What is Direct Mail Automation: /what-is-direct-mail-automation
  Guide to automated direct mail for B2B, including triggered campaigns and ROI metrics.

- What is Visitor Deanonymization: /what-is-visitor-deanonymization
  Technical guide to visitor deanonymization methods, accuracy, and legal compliance.

- What is Account-Based Marketing: /what-is-account-based-marketing
  Complete ABM guide including strategy, tools, and measurement.

## Competitor Comparisons

- Clearbit Alternatives: /blog/clearbit-reveal-alternative
  Best Clearbit alternatives after shutdown, including Cursive, Warmly, Leadfeeder, and RB2B.

- RB2B Alternatives: /blog/rb2b-alternative
  Top RB2B alternatives with pricing, match rates, and feature comparisons.

- Leadfeeder Alternatives: /blog/leadfeeder-alternative
  Best Leadfeeder alternatives for person-level visitor identification.

- Demandbase Alternatives: /blog/demandbase-alternative
  Affordable Demandbase alternatives for SMB and mid-market companies.

- Instantly Alternatives: /blog/instantly-alternative
  Cold email tools with built-in visitor identification.

- Smartlead Alternatives: /blog/smartlead-alternative
  Email outreach platforms with visitor tracking.

- Clay Alternatives: /blog/clay-alternative
  Easier data enrichment tools with outbound automation.

- Warmly vs Cursive: /blog/warmly-vs-cursive
  Head-to-head comparison of Warmly and Cursive visitor identification.

- Apollo vs Cursive: /blog/apollo-vs-cursive
  Visitor identification vs prospecting database comparison.

- ZoomInfo vs Cursive: /blog/zoominfo-vs-cursive
  Website visitor ID vs contact database comparison.

- 6sense vs Cursive: /blog/6sense-vs-cursive
  Affordable ABM alternative to 6sense.

- Cursive vs RB2B: /blog/cursive-vs-rb2b
  Detailed feature, pricing, and accuracy comparison.

- Cursive vs Leadfeeder: /blog/cursive-vs-leadfeeder
  Person-level vs company-level identification comparison.

- Cursive vs Clearbit: /blog/cursive-vs-clearbit
  Best Clearbit Reveal replacement.

- Cursive vs Instantly: /blog/cursive-vs-instantly
  Visitor ID + email outreach vs email-only tool.

- Cursive vs Demandbase: /blog/cursive-vs-demandbase
  SMB-friendly ABM alternative.

## Industries

- B2B Software: /industries/b2b-software
  How SaaS companies use Cursive to convert free trial users and demo visitors.

- Agencies: /industries/agencies
  How marketing and sales agencies use Cursive for client lead generation.

- Ecommerce: /industries/ecommerce
  How ecommerce companies identify and re-engage cart abandoners.

