NOTES FOR CLAUDE
All content must render server-side (no client-side only rendering)
Every page needs minimum 800 words (educational pages 2,500-3,000+)
Internal linking is CRITICAL - minimum 15 links per page
Schema markup must be in <head> before any client code
Test every change with curl commands
Prioritize Phase 1 (critical fixes) before any content work
Use the exact patterns shown in templates - don't deviate
When in doubt, reference existing working pages as examples
Mark each task complete only after verification passes
